NeoPop for Motorola E680(I) 0.02

NeoPop is an NeoGeo Pocket emulator for  Motorola E680(I) phone,
based on the excellent emulator  with the same name for  Windows
written by neopop_uk.

----------------------------------------------------------------

History:

0.02 (08-18-2005)

	* fix some graphics error
	  修正了一些图形错误
	* improve the compatibility consumedly
	  大大地提高了兼容度
	* improve the stability
	  稳定性有所提高
	* should be a bit faster (still slow)
	  稍许的提速 (依然很慢)

0.01 (08-16-2005)

	* support .ngc, .ngp, .npc & .zip roms
	  支持 .ngc, .ngp, .npc 及 .zip 格式的 rom 文件
	* a good graphic user interface
	  友好的图形用户界面
	* support full screen mode
	  支持全屏模式
	* take screen shot at anytime
	  即时抓图
	* support battery state
	  电池存档
	* save state at any time
	  即时存档
	
	* no sound
	  无声
	* low speed
	  低速
	* low compatibility
	  低兼容度
	* low stability
	  不够稳定

----------------------------------------------------------------

Usage:

Put your roms in directory  /mmc/mmca1/Game/NGPRoms,  or you can
edit neopop.conf to change the location.  The configuration file
neopop.conf lies in the same directory of your installation.
请将 ROM 文件放置在目录 /mmc/mmca1/Game/NGPRoms 中, 或者编辑配置
文件 neopop.conf 修改 ROM 文件的搜索路径.  文件 neopop.conf 位于
安装目录中.

Click button "Help" to get key and button information.
点击 "帮助" 按钮可获取按键与界面按钮的相关信息.

